{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This man ran through whatever savings he had and bought plywood from this man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plywood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In wartime, plywood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't lift a single piece of plywood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's huge like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet, whatever we produced was sold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all sold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was sold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day they used to bring Polish money and Russian money, and it was-- it was totally absurd.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Totally absurd.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no rhyme or reason to the human behavior.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the people just were-- it's mass psychosis, and that's how it-- and of course when the crunch came, they didn't run anyhow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but-- but if you would have stopped for one second to think, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- hold on to your money, no matter how little it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least maybe it's worth something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not-- not to buy immovable objects.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To such an extent the irrationality replaced rational thinking, rational human behavior, because suddenly the-- the-- the normal pattern of-- of-- of logic is giving way to a-- to a sort of-- of-- of perplexity that-- that has got no-- no beginning and no end and no rationale and no-- no logic in it whatsoever, and-- and suddenly the most logical, intelligent person behaves like a-- like-- like a senseless child.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How long did this situation continue unchallenged?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It continued-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can only say-- give-- give testimony to it because I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left in the 31st of December, 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my-- my New Year's outing, crossing the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only in terms of-- of social stratification.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not otherwise.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
